snippet.title: Marvel's Captain America: Civil War - Kellogg's VR Experience
snippet.description:
Join the biggest super hero battle of the year with Kellogg's Marvel's "Captain America: Civil War" VR app and get the film on Digital HD September 2 and 3D Blu-ray, Blu-ray, DVD, Digital SD and VOD September 13! ► Subscribe to Marvel: http://bit.ly/WeO3YJ

Get ready for the digital release of Marvel's Captain America: Civil War: http://bit.ly/2aMEEoq
